  <brief_title>Caudal Epidural Steroid Injections for Low Back Pain/Sciatic Lumbar Pain</brief_title>
  <acronym>FIA1</acronym>
  <official_title>Efficacy Study of Caudal Epidural Steroid Injections in Patients With Low Back Pain/Radiculopathy</official_title>
